# Drop your Android APK in this folder

Place your built APK file (e.g. `quotex-1.0.0.apk`) directly in this folder.
It will be served at `https://yourdomain.com/apk/quotex-1.0.0.apk` and the home
page will automatically list it as a downloadable version.

This folder is tracked in git (via this .gitkeep), so the APK persists across
redeploys. To add a new version:

  1. Build your APK
  2. Copy the .apk file here
  3. Commit + push to deploy

  git add public/apk/quotex-1.0.0.apk
  git commit -m "Add APK v1.0.0"
  git push

The home page at `/` detects the latest .apk by modification time and offers
it as the primary download button.
